the slogan is "making e commerce border agnostic"
it should solve the local issues like shipping payment legal returns stock ...
D2C direct to customer
there is the GDPR issue
places like Israel are using a supplier retailer it is a obstacle to the brand start working in D2C mode since that will kill the suppliers retail Business 

the key to succeed in D2V is to be globalize but still talk in local language patterns currencies and tax habits , return policy (3rd importance in shoppers choice of online shopping), business calendar (holiday and summer sales...)  others so the shoppers will still feel at home 


